{"tid":581912,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"RubberBand「H」大碟第二首派台歌《城市當代配樂團》","createTime":"2018-03-05T17:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T16:10:03.000Z","uid":4260,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"28eb52255f78f4e6ccafac197ad8767d92ba128a","tid":581912,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/28056820_10155201458396434_3587692768462737165_n.jpg?oh=0570b6d848b77521203ca3c53765f5d5&amp;oe=5B3E505D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F28056820_10155201458396434_3587692768462737165_n.jpg%3Foh%3D0570b6d848b77521203ca3c53765f5d5%26oe%3D5B3E505D&h=d350a750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自上年夏天推出「脫軌時刻」後， RubberBand推出第二首派台歌「城市當代配樂團」。RubberBand曾於不同場合提過，新專輯將由每首成員負責領軍兩首歌曲的製作，其他人則輔助完成。雖然外間往往會將樂隊視為一個單位，但畢竟四個獨立個體均有各自喜愛的聲音，於是大家一致希望在不影響樂隊風格的情況下，藉著這張專輯為樂迷呈現各自喜愛的聲音。「城市當代配樂團」由泥鯭監製，Tim Lui填詞，歌曲加入了Gospel的風格，整體靈感來自於某年樂隊接受一個主題為「為城市配樂」的訪問。由第一首歌到現在，RubberBand寫的歌大都是取材自我們成長的這個城市。<br />\n<br />\n在構思歌詞題材的時候，主音 6號提到：<br />\n「年月飛快，原來已經十年了，<br />\n當初的聽歌的中學生，今天也投身社會，<br />\n當年聽歌時尚在拍拖的一對，<br />\n可能家中也得了新成員；<br />\n當大家不知不覺光陰溜走的時候，一首歌正好帶回的當時回憶。」<br />\n<br />\nRubberBand表示製作這首歌曲的時候，最初只當是RubberBand的一個小回顧，然而接近尾聲時才發覺，這個城市的當代配樂團又豈止他們四人，一直以來都有很多音樂人和歌手默默為廣東歌而努力，為此他們更特別邀得同樣一直為在香港樂壇默默努力的歌手好友小肥和鄭嘉嘉為此歌配唱和音，以表達樂壇中每一位皆都是城市當代配樂團的意義！<br />\n<br />\n「你我他都哼過的，曾在這裡唱著的。」<br />\n<br />\n曲：RubberBand 詞：Tim Lui<br />\n編：RubberBand 監：泥鯭@RubberBand<br />\n<br />\n立即下載及收聽:<br />\niTunes: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/oEdJY3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FoEdJY3&d=o829%2FB34W68xjwZvhWLLH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4000e512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/oEdJY3</a><br />\nApple Music:<a href=\"https://goo.gl/njuQif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnjuQif&d=o829%2FB34W68xjwZvhWLLH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7728b2ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/njuQif</a><br />\nhmvPLAY: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/pBD26M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FpBD26M&d=o829%2FB34W68xjwZvhWLLH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5736edc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/pBD26M</a><br />\nJOOX: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/wuxb7q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fwuxb7q&d=o829%2FB34W68xjwZvhWLLH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=146c5baa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/wuxb7q</a><br />\nKKBOX: <a href=\"https://kkbox.fm/PSLNWi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkkbox.fm%2FPSLNWi&d=o829%2FB34W68xjwZvhWLLH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=598bfccc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kkbox.fm/PSLNWi</a><br />\nMOOV: <a href=\"https://s.moov.hk/r?s=ZL444L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.moov.hk%2Fr%3Fs%3DZL444L&d=o829%2FB34W68xjwZvhWLLH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=cae1aa92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.moov.hk/r?s=ZL444L</a><br />\nMusicOne: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/HQHCbQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FHQHCbQ&d=o829%2FB34W68xjwZvhWLLH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d2853d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/HQHCbQ</a><br />\nSpotify: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/ntvY2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FntvY2F&d=o829%2FB34W68xjwZvhWLLH%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e6e932e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ntvY2F</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9月尾開演唱會</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10eb07657ffc115ae4646060237d1e07f735a008","tid":581912,"uid":60166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"新碟個style幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"