core":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"RB成員‬泥鯭稱有自家釀製啤酒，計劃由現有的1種原味增至4款口味，以配合隊員數目和各自的特性，笑指自己最適合黑啤因佬味滿瀉；主唱6號就粉味重，因對方經常吃龍角散令嘴角滿是粉；辣味就非結他手阿正莫屬。自嘲麻辣一族的阿正即鬼馬稱Bass手阿偉就要奶味啤酒，因對方育有B女，必定奶味濃，逗得全場大笑。<br />\n<br />\nRB續指新款啤酒能否趕在9月的演唱會面世仍是未知數，不過就落實屆時發行新專輯，以紀念10年前的9月26日推出首張專輯及這10年間的創作路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836121a4cc4fdef18340a90c4a9c4d5003e9b586","tid":581912,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/215945_f99f00812912bc8e62a45f4543c6500b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F215945_f99f00812912bc8e62a45f4543c6500b.png&h=cb4cbd1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c156ba65e4954af01a7f29f142fea5953620be0","tid":581912,"uid":148742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:05:45.000Z","msg":"今個星期六op有無人去？"},{"pid":"12ee9a4537453d6f2fe8b5258b78a45c58e37c29","tid":581912,"uid":41455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c156ba65e4954af01a7f29f142fea5953620be0","tid":581912,"uid":148742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:05:45.000Z","msg":"今個星期六op有無人去？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"有沒有飛交人放飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2a95432aa7f5eeeb045d6949c278e91b5e2706","tid":581912,"uid":148742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12ee9a4537453d6f2fe8b5258b78a45c58e37c29","tid":581912,"uid":41455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c156ba65e4954af01a7f29f142fea5953620be0","tid":581912,"uid":148742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0